%20would%20be%20defeated%20in%20Telangana.%20However%2C%20electoral%20politics%20is%20a%20great%20leveller%20and%20data%20shows%20that%20KCR%2C%20still%20a%20phenomenon%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20was%20voted%20out%20by%20the%20rural%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2080%20of%20the%20119%20seats%20of%20Telangana%20classified%20as%20rural%2C%20the%20Congress%20trounced%20the%20BRS%20and%20won%2056%2C%20compared%20to%20only%2015%20in%202018.%20The%20BRS%20won%2062%20in%202018%2C%20but%20could%20manage%20only%2019%20this%20time%20-%20down%2043%20seats.%20Given%20that%2060%20is%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20rural%20win%20for%20the%20Congress%20is%20the%20singular%20factor%20that%20led%20to%20its%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20agrarian%20discontent%20-%20family%20rule%2C%20focus%20on%20Hyderabad%20added%20to%20the%20two-term%20anti-incumbency.%20It%20is%20not%20that%20the%20BRS%20government%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20for%20rural%20areas%2C%20just%20that%20their%20narrative%20of%20economic%20growth%20suggested%20a%20greater%20urban%20bias.%20Much%20like%20the%20way%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20was%20undone%20in%202004.%20Then%20it%20was%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20one%20who%20envisioned%20modern-day%20Hyderabad%20as%20a%20global%20city%2C%20who%20was%20undone%20by%20the%20rural%20voters.%20KCR%20and%20his%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20-%20the%20number%20two%20in%20his%20cabinet%20and%20the%20suave%20and%20erudite%20IT%20minister%20-%20have%20made%20the%20same%20mistake.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fhs3vet9o_telangana-rural-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Urban%20-%20Rural%20divide%20gets%20starker%20when%20you%20see%20the%20results%20in%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20region.%20Of%20the%2024%20seats%2C%20the%20BRS%20won%2016.%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20%C2%A0All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Musalmeen%20(AIMIM)%20had%20its%20stranglehold%20over%20seven%20seats%20in%20Hyderabad.%20The%20BJP%20could%20win%20only%20one%20seat%20and%20the%20Congress%20was%20routed.%20The%20Congress%20had%20won%20two%20seats%20in%202018%20and%20both%20the%20winners%20shifted%20to%20the%20BRS.%20They%20won%20as%20BRS%20candidates%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20eight%20urban%20seats%20outside%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20region%2C%20the%20Congress%20gained%20three%20seats%20and%20the%20BRS%20lost%20three.%20This%20may%20suggest%20that%20the%20more%20one%20moves%20out%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20weaker%20the%20BRS%20becomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Feep5ug68_telangana-urban-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F1qr28gag_telangana-greater-hyderabad-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20can%20be%20broadly%20divided%20into%20northern%20districts%20like%20Adilabad%2C%20Nizamabad%2C%20Warangal%20and%20Karimnagar%2C%20which%20are%20traditional%20BRS%20strongholds%2C%20and%20southern%20districts%20like%20Khammam%2C%20Nalgonda%20and%20Mahbubnagar%2C%20which%20are%20traditional%20Congress%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20northern%20districts%20were%20areas%20where%20Left%20parties%20had%20a%20strong%20presence.%20These%20later%20became%20the%20bastion%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20from%20which%20the%20KCR%20split%20to%20form%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20or%20TRS%20(later%20renamed%20as%20Bhartiya%20Rashtriya%20Samiti)%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20breached%20this%20BRS%20bastion.%20Of%20the%2017%20seats%20in%20the%20region%20-%20the%20BRS%20won%20all%20in%202018%20-%20the%20Congress%20won%20nine%20this%20time%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20three%2C%20reducing%20the%20BRS%20to%20five.%20The%20BJP%20is%20making%20inroads%20in%20this%20area%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20BRS.%20This%20is%20a%20major%20worry%20for%20the%20regional%20party%2C%20especially%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20three%20southern%20districts%20that%20have%20been%20analysed%2C%20the%20Congress%20swept%20all%2014%20seats%2C%20and%20the%20BRS%2C%20which%20won%20eight%20in%202018%2C%20was%20wiped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F5052dkjg_adilabad-nizamabad-karimnagar-warangal-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Foda7gj28_mahabubnagar-nalgonda-khammam-seats-table-ndtv_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20Congress%20swept%20its%20strongholds%20and%20raided%20into%20the%20BRS%20heartland%20along%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Only%20the%20capital%20city%20held%20firm%20with%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20solace%20for%20the%20BRS%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20just%20five%20more%20than%20the%20majority%20mark%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20nervousness%20within%20the%20national%20party%20over%20fears%20of%20poaching.%20The%20Congress%20will%20certainly%20spend%20its%20energies%20on%20keeping%20the%20flock%20together%2C%20with%20inherent%20contradictions%20within%20and%20many%20aspirants%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minster's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gives%20space%20to%20the%20BRS%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20strong%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20tough%20road%20ahead.%20The%20regional%20party%20is%20caught%20between%20the%20national%20might%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20resurgent%20Congress%20in%20the%20south%2C%20corruption%20allegations%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20case%20into%20Delhi%20liquor%20case%20allegations%20against%20KCR's%20daughter%20Kavitha%20Kalavakuntla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20KTR%20and%20KCR%20play%20their%20cards%20now%20could%20well%20determine%20the%20future%20of%20the%20regional%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(TM%20Veeraraghav%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701765480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fh8q25nso_k-chandrasekhar-rao-kcr_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkcr-won-urban-votes-but-congress-decimated-him-in-rural-areas-4635000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Six%20months%20ago%2C%20few%20leaders%2C%20even%20in%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20would%20have%20thought%20that%20the%20mighty%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20and%20his%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20would%20be%20defeated%20in%20Telangana.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkcr-won-urban-votes-but-congress-decimated-him-in-rural-areas-4635000%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%