ia%2Fchina-says-afghan-taliban-must-reform-before-full-diplomatic-ties%2Famp_articleshow%2F105751067.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Gives%20Army%20Four%20Months%20to%20Fix%20Policy%20on%20Promotion%20of%20Women%20Officers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20gave%20the%20Army%20four%20months%E2%80%99%20time%20to%20finalise%20its%20policy%20on%20promotion%20of%20women%20officers%20from%20the%20rank%20of%20colonel%20to%20brigadier%2C%20after%20it%20was%20told%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3Edeliberations%20on%20the%20issue%20are%20underway%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20took%20note%20of%20the%20submissions%20of%20Attorney%20General%20(AG)%20R.%20Venkataramani%20and%20senior%20advocate%20R.%20Balasubramanian%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECJI%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20give%20you%20%5BArmy%5D%20time%20for%20bringing%20the%20policy.%20We%20would%20expect%20the%20formulation%20of%20policy%20by%20March%2031%2C%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20women%20officers%20in%20the%20Army%20had%20alleged%20discrimination%20in%20promotion%20from%20the%20rank%20of%20colonel%20to%20brigadier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20February%2C%202020%20verdict%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20ordered%20permanent%20commission%20(PC)%20for%20women%20officers%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20rejecting%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20their%20%E2%80%9Cphysiological%20limitations%E2%80%9D%20as%20being%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Csex%20stereotypes%E2%80%9D%20and%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cgender%20discrimination%20against%20women%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Hindustan%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20said%20that%20all%20women%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20(SSC)%20had%20to%20be%20considered%20for%20permanent%20commission%20irrespective%20of%20them%20having%20completed%2014%20years%20or%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%2020%20years%20of%20service%20within%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20after%20that%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20the%20Navy%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20It%20had%20said%20that%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20would%20ensure%20women%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20overcome%20%E2%80%9Chistories%20of%20discrimination%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20March%2C%202020%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAG%20Venkatramani%20told%20the%20court%20that%20an%20officer%20must%20meet%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cessential%20eligibility%20criteria%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20minimum%202%20confidential%20reports%20in%20Colonel%20Select%20rank.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20deviation%20from%20this%20fundamental%20eligibility%20criteria%20will%20amount%20to%20compromising%20with%20the%20operational%20requirement%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20to%20earn%20the%20rank%20of%20brigadier%2C%20an%20Army%20officer%20is%20required%20to%20experience%20operational%20command%20of%20a%20unit%20or%20battalion%20for%20a%20period%20of%20nearly%202%20years.%20This%20experience%20and%20service%20knowledge%20as%20commanding%20officer%20of%20a%20unit%20helps%20officers%20to%20understand%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintricacies%2C%20nuances%20and%20complexities%E2%80%9D%20of%20command%2C%20Venkataramani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicant%20officers%2C%20represented%20by%20advocate%20Archana%20Pathak%20Dave%2C%20informed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3Ewomen%20have%20fought%20a%20long%20drawn%20battle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20courts%20to%20get%20their%20due.%20They%20said%20that%20command%20roles%20were%20made%20available%20to%20women%20only%20after%20the%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%202020%20decision%20on%20considering%20SSC%20women%20officers%20for%20PC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202021%2C%20the%20court%20found%20that%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20yardstick%20to%20grant%20PC%20to%20women%20officers%20was%20discriminatory%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20criteria%20for%20male%20officers.%20Dave%20said%20that%20the%20applicants%20only%20seek%20a%20policy%20to%20be%20put%20in%20place%20for%20governing%20promotions%20by%20special%20board%203%20(SB-3)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fform-policy-on-women-officers-promotion-sc-101701715027671.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20countered%20this%20by%20saying%20that%20all%20Army%20policies%20are%20%E2%80%9Cgender-neutral%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20applicants%20should%20not%20push%20the%20matter%20beyond%20a%20certain%20point.%20He%20said%20most%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20before%20the%20court%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%20for%20brigadier%20with%20command%20positions%20given%20to%20them%20after%20June%20this%20year%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20all%20because%20we%20pushed%20the%20envelope.%20We%20nudged%20you%2C%20otherwise%20nothing%20would%20have%20happened.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Court%20told%20Venkataramani%20that%20the%20Army%20had%20shown%20resistance%20by%20citing%20operational%20efficiency%20as%20a%20ground%20to%20justify%20denial%20of%20permanent%20commission%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20your%20case%20that%20operational%20preparedness%20of%20Army%20has%20been%20affected%20in%20any%20manner%20with%20women%20coming%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20submitted%20to%20Court%2C%20the%20AG%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20experience%20of%20performing%20in%20colonel%E2%80%99s%20rank%20is%20utmost%20essential%20to%20gauge%20any%20officer%E2%80%99s%20fitness%20for%20higher%20appointment.%20Any%20exception%20to%20this%20will%20have%20ramifications%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20leadership%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20along%20with%20opening%20avenues%20for%20many%20others%20who%20are%20deficient%20of%20command%20criteria%20to%20seek%20similar%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-pulls-up-army-for-denying-promotion-to-women-pc-officers-101699022243953.html%5C%22%3Etop%20court%20had%20criticised%20the%20Army%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20denying%20promotions%20to%20women%20permanent%20commission%20officers%20in%20November%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-pulls-up-army-for-denying-promotion-to-women-pc-officers-101699022243953.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20attitude%20has%20been%20to%20find%20some%20way%20to%20defeat%20the%20just%20entitlements%20of%20women%20officers.%20Such%20an%20approach%20does%20disservice%20to%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20justice%20to%20the%20women%20officers%2C%20who%20have%20already%20fought%20a%20long%20and%20hard%20battle%2C%20to%20get%20their%20just%20entitlements%20under%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20officers%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20last%20year%20as%20SB-3%20that%20empanels%20officers%20as%20colonel%20had%20not%20met%20for%2018%20months%20despite%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%202021%20directive%20to%20the%20Army%20asking%20it%20to%20grant%20all%20consequential%20benefits%20including%20promotion%20and%20financial%20benefits%20to%20the%20women%20officers%20within%203%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701765331000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-gives-army-four-months-to-fix-policy-on-promotion-of-women-officers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20women%20officers%20in%20the%20Army%20had%20alleged%20discrimination%20in%20promotion%20from%20the%20rank%20of%20colonel%20to%20brigadier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-gives-army-four-months-to-fix-policy-on-promotion-of-women-officers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Rohit%20the%20skipper%20needed%20more%20than%20Rohit%20the%20batter'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701765328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105750964%2Cimgsize-52450.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Frohit-the-skipper-needed-more-than-rohit-the-batter-says-mohammad-kaif%2Farticleshow%2F105750821.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20a%20hard-fought%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20where%20India's%20dreams%20were%20shattered%20by%20the%20Australians%20in%20the%20title%20match%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20cricketing%20world%20now%20shifts%20its%20focus%20to%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20As%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20looms%2C%20the%20question%20arises%3A%20Will%20Rohit%20Sharma%20continue%20to%20lead%20the%20Indian%20side%2C%20or%20will%20a%20new%20captain%20step%20up%3F%20For%20Kaif%2C