rease%20in%20torrent%20site%20downloads.%20However%2C%20experts%20warn%20about%20the%20risks%2C%20including%20malware%2C%20viruses%2C%20spyware%2C%20adware%2C%20fake%20torrent%20files%2C%20poor%20quality%2C%20slow%20speeds%2C%20network%20strain%2C%20device%20overheating%2C%20and%20data%20loss.%20Safer%20alternatives%20to%20torrenting%20include%20waiting%20for%20the%20official%20release%20on%20streaming%20platforms%20or%20renting%20the%20movie%20from%20reputable%20online%20platforms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mizoram%20Election%20Results%20Usher%20in%20New%20Politics%20and%20Developmental%20Challenges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05131251%2FFKNdrT2VEAM9zbg.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAizawl%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20election%20results%20for%20the%20ninth%20Mizoram%20assembly%20elections%20are%20of%20great%20significance%20for%20the%20state.%20In%20the%20electoral%20history%20of%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20there%20has%20never%20been%20a%20situation%20where%20a%20mandate%20was%20for%20a%20hung%20assembly%20or%20for%20a%20coalition%20government.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20tradition%20of%20a%20government%20being%20formed%20either%20by%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20regional%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20has%20come%20to%20a%20close.%20A%20new%20and%20a%20third%20political%20party%20has%20been%20given%20a%20clear%20mandate%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-year-old%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20has%20been%20given%20a%20huge%20mandate%20by%20the%20voters.%20In%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections%2C%20though%20the%20ZPM%20was%20attracting%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20as%20a%20new%20party%2C%20it%20could%20win%20only%20six%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20MNF%20stole%20the%20show%20with%2027%20seats.%20The%20scenario%20has%20changed%20these%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20the%20ZPM%20that%20won%2027%20seats%2C%20leaving%20the%20MNF%20with%20just%20ten%20seats.%20C.%20Ngunlianchunga%20has%20won%20the%20only%20seat%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lawngtlai%20West%20Rural%3B%20he%20has%20won%20that%20seat%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Congress%20presence%20in%20the%2040-member%20assembly%20has%20shrunk%20to%20one%20from%20five%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20increase%20its%20tally%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20two%20wins.%20This%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20had%2020.82%25%20votes%20and%20BJP%20only%205.06%25%20votes.%20Still%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20seats%20won%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20party%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20third%20position%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ZPM%20got%2037.86%25%20of%20the%20votes%20polled%2C%20MNF%20got%2035.10%25.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20which%20also%20tried%20its%20luck%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20along%20with%20NOTA%20and%20independents%20got%20a%20total%20of%201.14%25%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20also%20significant%20about%20these%20election%20results%20is%2C%20three%20women%20MLAs%20were%20elected%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20border%20state.%20While%20two%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20the%20ZPM%20(Lalrinpuii%20from%20the%20Lunglei%20East%20seat%20and%20Baryl%20Wenneihsangi%20from%20Aizawl%20South-3%20seat)%2C%20Prova%20Chakma%20of%20the%20MNF%20bagged%20the%20Tuipui%20West%20seat.%20While%20Prova%20Chakma%20defeated%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20to%20become%20the%20first%20woman%20MLA%20from%20the%20Chakma%20community%2C%20Baryl%20Venneihsangi%2C%20a%20popular%20news%20anchor%2C%20defeated%20an%20MNF%20candidate%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%20In%202014%2C%20a%20Congresswoman%20had%20won%20a%20by-election%20and%20entered%20the%20assembly%20after%2027%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20noteworthy%20fact%20from%20the%20poll%20results%20is%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%2C%20Zoramthanga%20of%20MNF.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20history%2C%20whenever%20a%20ruling%20party%20loses%20elections%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20defeated%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20needs%20highlighting%20is%20also%20this%3A%20while%20the%20ZPM%20had%20a%20good%20show%20mostly%20in%20the%20urban%20pockets%20%E2%80%93%20it%20won%20all%20the%2012%20seats%20in%20Aizawl%20City%2C%20four%20in%20Lunglei%20and%20all%20three%20in%20Serchhip%20%E2%80%93%20the%20MNF%20won%20all%2010%20seats%20in%20the%20rural%20areas.%20The%20BJP%20has%20won%20one%20seat%20from%20the%20Chakma%20region.%20The%20Congress%20and%20BJP%C2%A0have%20won%20seats%20in%20Saiha%20and%20Lawngtlai%20districts%20of%20south%20Mizoram.%20BJP%20has%20won%20two%20seats%20in%C2%A0Saiha%20district%20and%20Congress%20has%20won%20one%20of%20the%20two%20seats%20in%20Lawngtlai%20district.%20BJP%20has%20won%20both%C2%A0the%20seats%20of%20the%20Mara%20tribal%20community%20and%20Congress%20has%20won%20one%20seat%20from%20the%20Lai%20tribal%20community%20area%20of%20Lawngtlai%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20specificities%2C%20these%20elections%20are%20important%20for%20the%20main%20political%20players%20of%20the%20state%20in%20many%20ways.%20The%20ruling%20party%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20return%20to%20power.%20The%20ZPM%20created%20important%20history%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%20also%20registered%20a%20big%20fall%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20a%20big%20rise%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20political%20leaders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20question%20is%2C%20how%20will%20this%20election%20impact%20Zoramthanga%E2%80%99s%20supremacy%20within%20the%20MNF%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20ZPM%2C%20it%20will%20be%20challenging%20for%20Lalduhoma%20to%20keep%20together%20the%20two%20factions%20of%20ex-Congress%20and%20ex-MNF%20leaders%20who%20had%20shifted%20to%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Congress%2C%20post%20its%20poor%20show%2C%20the%20leadership%20of%20state%20president%20Lalsawta%20will%20likely%20face%20a%20serious%20challenge%20from%20the%20supporters%20of%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20Lalthanhawla%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20questions%20thrown%20up%20by%20the%20December%204%20results%20have%20made%20this%20election%20important%20for%20politicians%20in%20many%20ways.%20Lalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20long%20wait%20for%20the%20political%20limelight%20is%20finally%20over%3B%20he%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20chair%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20in%20the%20state.%20If%20the%20ZPM%20was%20not%20to%20win%20this%20time%20around%2C%20Lalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20political%20future%20would%20likely%20have%20been%20eclipsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Lalduhoma%20is%20set%20to%20rise%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20political%20innings%20of%20MNF%20supremo%20Zoramthanga%20have%20most%20likely%20come%20to%20an%20end.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%20he%20will%20fight%20another%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20BJP%2C%20due%20to%20the%20defeat%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20new%20leader%20Lalrinliana%20Sailo%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20his%20future%20in%20the%20party%20has%20become%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20with%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZPM%20leader%20and%20chief%20ministererial%20candidate%20Lalduhoma%2C%20while%20talking%20to%20the%20media%20after%20winning%20the%20elections%20on%20December%204%2C%20said%20that%20zero%20tolerance%20on%20state%20corruption%2C%20bringing%20about%20financial%20reforms%2C%20balanced%20development%20in%20the%20state%2C%20investigation%20of%20corruption%20cases%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20engaging%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20Zo-unification%20(with%20the%20Kukis%20and%20Maras%20of%20neighbouring%20Manipur)%20are%20going%20to%20be%20the%20main%20priorities%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20fulfil%20the%20big%20promises%20ZPM%20had%20made%20to%20the%20voters%2C%20including%20on%20the%20Zo-unification%20issue.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20for%20the%20new%20government%20will%20also%20be%20to%20bring%20financial%20mismanagement%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ZPM%20is%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20BJP-led%20North%20East%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NEDA)%20and%20the%20NDA%2C%20as%20Mizoram%20is%20dependent%20on%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20for%20its%20economic%20needs.%20And%20there%20could%20be%20more%20to%20it%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20has%20won%20handsomely%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own%2C%20the%20ZPM%20is%20already%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20induct%20at%20least%20one%20of%20its%20MLAs%20into%20the%20new%20government.%20If%20a%20regional%20party%20runs%20a%20state%20government%2C%20it%20has%20to%20somewhat%20compromise%20to%20establish%20some%20sort%20of%20harmony%20and%20working%20relations%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20particularly%20so%20when%20it%20is%20financially%20dependent%20on%20it.%20Along%20with%20its%20Christian%20politics%2C%20ZPM%20will%20also%20then%20have%20to%20maintain%20an%20equilibrium%20of%20sorts%20with%20the%20Hindutva%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Church%20organisations%20have%20influence%20on%20the%20politics%20of%20Mizoram.%20The%20two%20BJP%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Mara%20community%2C%20who%20are%20Christian%20too%2C%20will%20also%20then%20face%20the%20challenge%20of%20forging%20a%20rapport%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20times%20to%20come%2C%20it%20will%20be%20seen%20how%20this%20working%20relationship%20of%20the%20ZPM%20in%20general%20with%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20Mara%20MLAs%20in%20particular%20with%20the%20national%20party%2C%20will%20pan%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESuwa%20Lal%20Jangu%20is%20assistant%20professor%20of%20political%20science%2C%20Mizoram%20University%2C%20Aizawl.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701762266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05131251%2FFKNdrT2VEAM9zbg.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-election-results-usher-in-new-politics-and-developmental-challenges%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20break%20from%20history%2C%20the%20six-year-old%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20has%20been%20given%20a%20huge%20mandate%20by%20the%20voters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-election-results-usher-in-new-politics-and-developmental-challenges%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Was%20Lakhbir%20Singh%20Rode%2C%20Pak-Based%20Khalistani%20Terrorist%20Wanted%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKhalistani%20terrorist%20Lakhbir%20Singh%20Rode%20has%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20said%20intelligence%20sources.%20He%20was%2072.%C2%A0Lakhbir%20Singh%20Rode%2C%20an%20accused%20in%20the%201985%20bombing%20of%20Air%20India%20jet%20Kanishka%2C%20was%20listed%20as%20a%20terrorist%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20for%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhindranwale%20Connect%20And%20Life%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhbir%20Singh%20Rode%20was%20the%20nephew%20of%20Jarnail%20Singh%20Bhindranwale%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20during%201984%20Operation%20Blue%20Star%20at%20Amritsar's%20Golden%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20from%20Rode%20village%20in%20Moga%20district%20of%20Punjab.%20Lakhbir%20Singh%20initially%20moved%20to%20Dubai%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Jarnail%20Singh%20Bhindranwale%2C%20and%20later%20relocated%20to%20Pakistan.%20His%20family%20stays%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesignated%20Terrorist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhbir%20Singh%20Rode%20was%20the%20self-styled%20head%20of%20the%20banned%20outfits%20Khalistan%20Liberation%20Force%20(KLF)%20and%20the%20International%20Sikh%20Youth%20Federation%20(ISYF).%20Sources%20say%20Rode%20worked%20with%20Pakistan's%20intelligence%20agency%20ISI%20closely%20to%20carry%20out%20terror%20activities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2C%20the%20UK%20banned%20Lakhbir%20Singh%20Rode's%20ISYF%20in%202001%2C%20the%20US%20banned%20it%20a%20year%20later.%20Following%20the%20ban%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20group%20changed%20its%20name%20to%20Sikh%20Federation-UK%20(SFU).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ENIA%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20court%20in%20Punjab's%20Mohali%20had%20ordered%20the%20confiscation%20of%20land%20belonging%20to%20the%20designated%20terrorist%20in%20Moga%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20had%20charged%20him%20with%20smuggling%20drugs%20and%20explosives%20to%20India%20from%20Pakistan%20for%20triggering%20blasts%20across%20Punjab.%20He%20is%20also%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20plots%20to%20assassinate%20prominent%20personalities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20was%20also%20registered%20against%20him%20for%20masterminding%20a%20tiffin%20blast%20in%20Punjab's%20Fazilka%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701762180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3ratafr_lakhbir-singh-rode_625x300_05_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjarnail-singh-bhindranwale-lakhbir-singh-rode-who-was-lakhbir-singh-rode-pak-based-khalistani-ter