emocratic%20principles%20should%20%E2%80%9Ccome%20forward%20to%20ensure%20that%20Sikhs%20and%20all%20Indian%20minority%20communities%20living%20in%20the%20US%20are%20safe%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20transnational%20repression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20highlighted%20the%20alleged%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20citizen%2C%20in%20Vancouver%20in%20June.%20Jakara%20Movement%20recounted%20that%20the%20FBI%20had%20warned%20several%20other%20Sikhs%20in%20the%20US%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20that%20their%20lives%20could%20be%20in%20danger%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20at%20least%20one%20documented%20instance%20in%20recent%20months%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20operative%20surveilling%20a%20Sikh%20house%20of%20worship%20in%20the%20US%20and%20then%20demanding%20information%20from%20a%20religious%20leader%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSikhs%20and%20all%20Americans%20living%20in%20the%20U.S.%20should%20be%20able%20to%20practice%20their%20constitutional%20and%20human%20rights%20without%20experiencing%20repression%20from%20a%20foreign%20power.%20They%20must%20be%20able%20to%20gather%2C%20protest%20and%20speak%20out%2C%20free%20from%20intimidation%2C%20harassment%2C%20surveillance%20and%20violence%20from%20other%20nations%20and%20their%20agents%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sikh%20groups%20requested%20all%20democratic%20organisations%20and%20citizens%20to%20build%20pressure%20on%20the%20US%20government%2C%20suggesting%20the%20following%20steps%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Express%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20other%20affected%20Indian%20minority%20communities%20in%20the%20US%20through%20statements%2C%20letters%20and%20online%20posts%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Convene%20conversations%20about%20authoritarianism%20and%20human%20rights%20in%20India%20at%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20libraries%20and%20other%20centers%20featuring%20impacted%20communities%2C%20activists%20and%20scholars%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Demand%20the%20DOJ%20be%20fully%20transparent%20about%20the%20investigation%2C%20unseal%20all%20indictments%20and%20prosecute%20all%20those%20responsible%20no%20matter%20how%20senior%20their%20position%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Demand%20the%20US%20government%20sanction%20any%20individuals%20and%20entities%20employed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20found%20to%20be%20responsible%20or%20connected%20to%20the%20foiled%20plot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Call%20on%20state%20legislative%20bodies%20and%20Congress%20to%20hold%20hearings%20on%20transnational%20repression%20that%20include%20discussion%20of%20India%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Call%20on%20Congress%20to%20pass%20and%20President%20Biden%20to%20sign%20the%20Transnational%20Repression%20Policy%20Act%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Urge%20the%20US%20to%20honor%20its%20commitments%20as%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20Declaration%20of%20Principles%20to%20Combat%20Transnational%20Repression%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20Urge%20the%20US%20and%20other%20democracies%20to%20better%20coordinate%20on%20combating%20transnational%20repression%2C%20including%20imposing%20penalties%20like%20sanctions%2C%20diplomatic%20expulsions%20and%20criminal%20charges%3B%20and%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20Insist%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20cooperate%20fully%20with%20all%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701759922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26162627%2Fsandy-millar-UfY8CbyIwRg-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsikhs-america-community-groups-transparency-pannun-plot%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20groups%20issued%20a%20series%20of%20suggestions%20to%20build%20pressure%2C%20including%20calling%20on%20state%20legislative%20bodies%20and%20Congress%20to%20hold%20hearings%20on%20%26quot%3Btransnational%20re