Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20will%20be%20Congress.%20That%20is%20why%2C%20even%20two%20days%20after%20crossing%20the%20magic%20figure%20in%20Telangana%2C%20they%20have%20not%20elected%20a%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%20leader%2C%20who%20goes%20on%20to%20become%20Chief%20Minister.%20Nor%20could%20they%20proceed%20with%20an%20oath%20ceremony%20as%20planned%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20red%20carpet%20had%20been%20laid.%20The%20chairs%20for%20the%20venue%20were%20wrapped%20in%20white.%20The%20sound%20systems%20and%20equipment%20were%20set%20up.%20Even%20the%20flowers%20had%20been%20ordered.%20It%20was%20all%20dismantled%20because%20the%20Congress%20displayed%20the%20marks%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%20DNA%26quot%3B%20and%20behaved%20as%20many%20expect%20it%20to%20behave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20throughout%20the%20campaign%20and%20the%20victory%2C%20it%20had%20seemed%20obvious%20that%20Telangana%20Congress%20chief%20Revanth%20Reddy%20was%20the%20leading%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20face%20and%20voice%20of%20the%20campaign%2C%20buttressed%20by%20the%20support%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20stretch%20to%20assume%20that%20he%20would%20be%20chief%20minister%2C%20if%20not%20a%20front-runner%2C%20by%20a%20mile.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20never%20going%20to%20be%20that%20easy%2C%20considering%20the%20grand%20old%20party's%20long%20history%20of%20vocal%20leaders%20and%20aspirants.%20Those%20who%20have%20been%20with%20the%20party%20for%20years%20thought%20this%20is%20the%20time%20to%20collect%2C%20remind%20the%20leadership%20that%20they%20are%20the%20original%20warhorses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20voices%20of%20protest%20within%2C%20from%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20to%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%2C%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%20to%20Damodar%20Rajanarasimha.%20They%20reportedly%20opposed%20the%20outright%20candidature%20of%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20leaders%20allege%20Revanth%20Reddy%20floated%20the%20theory%20that%20he%20was%20the%20popular%20choice%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20MLAs%2C%20that%20compromise%20formulas%20had%20been%20worked%20out%20to%20make%20him%20chief%20minister%20and%20accommodate%20other%20senior%20leaders%20as%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20or%20ministers%20with%20plum%20portfolios.%20They%20also%20pointed%20at%20Revanth%20Reddy's%20%26quot%3Binexperience%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20always%20been%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20never%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20is%20familiar%20with%20attacks%20from%20within.%20Even%20when%20he%20was%20made%20state%20Congress%20chief%2C%20some%20of%20his%20colleagues%20suggested%20he%20had%20paid%20crores%20for%20the%20post.%20This%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20a%20virtual%20write-off%2C%20not%20even%20in%20contention.%20Again%2C%20when%20candidates%20were%20being%20chosen%2C%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20%26quot%3Bselling%20tickets%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20had%20pushed%20hard%20to%20get%20his%20men%20picked%20as%20candidates.%20He%20knew%20only%20too%20well%20that%20if%20he%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20numbers%2C%20he%20wouldn't%20stand%20a%20chance%20within%20his%20own%20party.%20Now%2C%20his%20supporters%20point%20out%20that%20he%20has%20as%20many%20as%2042%20MLAs%20backing%20him%2C%20and%20that%20denying%20him%20the%20top%20job%20would%20stir%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leadership%20arranged%20meetings%20with%20each%20of%20the%20party's%2064%20MLAs%20to%20glean%20the%20real%20picture.%C2%A0Separate%20meetings%20were%20also%20held%20with%20various%20leaders%20to%20try%20and%20work%20out%20a%20formula.%20Predictably%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20to%20leave%20the%20decision%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20command%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E61-year-old%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20has%20always%20been%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20has%20won%20seven%20elections%2C%20including%20as%20MP%20from%20Nalgonda.%20He%20was%20an%20Air%20Force%20fighter%20pilot%20and%20is%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20having%20been%20an%20associate%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20He's%20%26quot%3Bmost%20qualified%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20chief%20minister%2C%20said%20a%20source%20close%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%20chief%20Mallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%2C%2063%2C%20belongs%20to%20the%20Mala%20group%20of%20the%20Dalit%20community.%20Vikramarka%20has%20been%20a%20three-time%20MLA%2C%20has%20served%20as%20deputy%20speaker%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition.%20He%20is%20the%20brother%20of%20Mallu%20Ravi%20who%2C%20however%2C%20has%20declared%20his%20support%20for%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%20went%20on%20a%201%2C400-kilometre%20march%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20so%20he%20can%20claim%20to%20have%20campaigned%20for%20the%20party%20beyond%20his%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKomatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%2C%2058%2C%20says%20he%20is%20among%20the%20senior%20most%20in%20the%20party%20with%20some%2035%20years%20in%20politics.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20former%20minister%2C%20four-time%20MLA%20and%20MP%2C%20and%20delivered%2011%20of%2012%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20his%20district%20of%20erstwhile%20Nalgonda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamodar%20Rajanarasimha%2C%20who%20turns%2065%20today%2C%20belongs%20to%20the%20dominant%20Madiga%20Scheduled%20Caste%20group.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20YS%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20cabinet%20and%20deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Kiran%20Kumar%20Reddy.%20His%20family%20has%20been%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%202004%2C%20before%20YS%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20after%20a%201%2C500-km%20padyatra%20that%20was%20seen%20to%20have%20la