hagwat%20Karad%20said%20in%20a%20written%20response.%20The%20process%20of%20recovery%20of%20dues%20from%20the%20borrower%20in%20written-off%20loan%20accounts%20continues%2C%20write-off%20does%20not%20benefit%20the%20borrower%2C%20Karad%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20the%20minister%20did%20not%20name%20individual%20borrowers%20whose%20accounts%20have%20been%20written%20off%20citing%20the%20RBI%20Act.%20Quoting%20RBI%2C%20he%20said%20that%20all%20SCBs%20have%20collected%20an%20aggregate%20amount%20of%20Rs%205%2C309.80%20crore%20as%20penal%20charges%2C%20including%20penalty%20charges%20against%20delay%20in%20payment%20of%20loans%2C%20during%20the%20financial%20year%202022-%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20another%20question%2C%20Karad%20said%20that%20SCBs%20and%20All%20India%20Financial%20Institutions%20report%20certain%20credit%20information%20of%20all%20borrowers%20having%20aggregate%20exposure%20of%20Rs.%205%20crore%20and%20above%20to%20the%20Central%20Repository%20of%20Information%20on%20Large%20Credits%20(CRILC).%20%E2%80%9CAs%20reported%20in%20CRILC%20database%2C%20as%20on%2031.3.2023%2C%20total%202%2C623%20unique%20borrowers%20were%20classified%20as%20wilful%20defaulters%2C%20with%20aggregate%20outstanding%20of%20over%20Rs%201.96%20lakh%20crore%20by%20SCBs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20clarified%20that%20the%20primary%20regulatory%20objective%20behind%20allowing%20wilful%20defaulters%20to%20enter%20into%20compromise%20settlement%20is%20to%20enable%20multiple%20avenues%20for%20lenders%20to%20recover%20the%20money%20in%20default%20without%20much%20delay.%20Apart%20from%20the%20time%20value%20loss%2C%20inordinate%20delays%20result%20in%20asset%20value%20deterioration%2C%20hampers%20ultimate%20recoveries%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701756934000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16101457%2Frupee-gb36195718_19