%20it%20to%20crash%20so%20he%20could%20make%20a%20YouTube%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Olympic%20snowboarder's%20video%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20Crashed%20My%20Plane%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20viewed%20over%204.4%20million%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he's%20been%20sentenced%20by%20California%20judge%20John%20F.%20Walter%20after%20pleading%20guilty%20in%20June%20to%20one%20count%20of%20destroying%20and%20concealing%20evidence%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20obstruct%20a%20federal%20investigation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-cdca%2Fpr%2Fsanta-barbara-county-man-sentenced-6-months-prison-obstructing-federal-probe-plane%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLOS%2520ANGELES%2520%25E2%2580%2593%2520A%2520YouTuber%2520pilot%2CCounty%2520to%2520gain%2520online%2520views.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20office%20for%20the%20Central%20District%20of%20California.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20orchestrated%20the%20crash%20on%20November%2024%2C%202021%2C%20setting%20off%20from%20the%20Lompoc%20City%20Airport%20toward%20Mammoth%20Lakes%2C%20per%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jacob%20didn't%20intend%20to%20reach%20his%20destination%2C%20and%20instead%20parachuted%20from%20his%20airplane%20after%20pretending%20it%20lost%20power%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe'd%20fitted%20his%20plane%20with%20multiple%20cameras%2C%20and%20recorded%20himself%20parachuting%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20Jacob%20informed%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20of%20the%20plane%20crash%2C%20and%20said%20he%20would%20help%20them%20locate%20the%20crashed%20plane%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20December%2010%2C%202021%2C%20he%20flew%20by%20helicopter%20with%20a%20friend%20to%20transport%20the%20wreck%20to%20a%20trailer%20attached%20to%20Jacob's%20pickup%20truck%2C%20then%20to%20a%20Lompoc%20City%20Airport%20hangar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20later%20disassembled%20the%20plane%20and%20dumped%20its%20parts%20into%20various%20trash%20bins%20at%20airport%2C%20which%20prosecutors%20said%20was%20done%20to%20obstruct%20a%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20investigation%20into%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20published%20his%20video%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20and%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftrevor-jacob-influencer-pilot-under-investigation-accused-staging-crash-youtube-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equickly%20subjected%20to%20intense%20scrutiny%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20other%20aviation%20YouTubers%20who%20questioned%20his%20choice%20of%20parachute%2C%20why%20he%20didn't%20radio%20for%20help%2C%20and%20why%20he%20chose%20to%20jump%20immediately%20instead%20of%20attempting%20a%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20pleading%20guilty%20in%20June%2C%20Jacob%20said%20he'd%20agreed%20to%20advertise%20a%20sponsor's%20product%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wallet%20%E2%80%94%20in%20his%20YouTube%20video%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob's%20video%20features%20him%20hiking%20after%20the%20crash%20for%20several%20hours%20through%20the%20dry%20brush%20of%20the%20Los%20Padres%20forest%20hills%2C%20eventually%20coming%20across%20his%20wrecked%20plane.%20The%20video%20ends%20with%20him%20meeting%20an%20unidentified%20person%20whom%20he%20said%20was%20a%20rancher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETrevor%20Jacob%20re-obtains%20his%20pilot's%20license%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20sentencing%2C%20Jacob%20released%20another%20video%20on%20Monday%20evening%20titled%20%26quot%3BI%20Got%20My%20Pilots%20License%20Back!%20But%20I'm%20Going%20To%20Prison.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20license%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Finfluencer-pilot-trevor-jacob-crashed-plane-on-purpose-faa-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevoked%20by%20the%20FAA%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D55JdKOFIecc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Monday%20video%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20shot%20before%20Jacob's%20sentencing%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20features%20him%20cooking%20eggs%2C%20skateboarding%2C%20sparring%20in%20jiu-jitsu%2C%20flying%20a%20plane%2C%20and%20riding%20a%20dirt%20bike%20as%20he%20expressed%20regret%20for%20his%20actions%2C%20describing%20himself%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bidiot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20video%2C%20he%20wore%20a%20t-shirt%20advertising%20his%20sports%20apparel%20and%20merchandise%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20athlete%20alleged%20he%20covered%20up%20evidence%20of%20the%20crash%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Breally%20bad%20legal%20advice%26quot%3B%20and%20intentionally%20crashed%20the%20plane%20not%20for%20clout%2C%20but%20because%20it%20was%20a%20childhood%20dream%20of%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20bucket%20list%20goal%2C%20I%20always%20told%20myself%20that%20before%20I%20die%2C%20I%20will%20jump%20out%20of%20a%20plane%20and%20watch%20it%20crash%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20pull%20my%20parachute%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20do%20it%20and%20I'll%20share%20it%20with%20the%20world%20and%20see%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20here%20we%20are.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you%20live%20and%20learn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20did%20not%20address%20why%20he%20had%20pretended%20the%20plane%20lost%20power%20in%20his%202021%20video%20and%20his%20aircraft%20accident%20incident%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20released%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20Business%20Insider%20through%20his%20attorney%2C%20where%20he%20called%20his%20experience%20%26quot%3Bso%20humbling%26quot%3B%20and%20thanked%20his%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20that%20Judge%20Walter%20considered%20many%20different%20aspects%20of%20my%20unique%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20he%20made%20the%20