or%20six%20years%20in%20its%20business%20and%20first-class%20cabins.%20He%20had%20been%20celebrating%20his%20birthday%20at%20Claw%20BBQ%2C%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Doha%2C%20in%20May%2C%20when%20he%20was%20approached%20by%20the%20officer%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20he%20and%20another%20flight%20attendant%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20police%20station%20after%20one%20of%20two%20officers%20wiped%20tinted%20moisturizer%20off%20their%20faces%20with%20wet%20wipes.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20skin%20product%20was%20from%20the%20Shiseido%20Men%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20the%20officer%20didn't%20ask%20for%20his%20consent%20to%20remove%20the%20moisturizer%20and%20continued%20to%20accuse%20him%20of%20being%20a%20sex%20worker%2C%20asking%20how%20much%20money%20he%20made%20every%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20the%20officer%20who%20approached%20him%20also%20pointed%20out%20his%20designer%20shoes%2C%20belt%2C%20and%20bag%2C%20and%20insisted%20that%20he%20must%20be%20a%20sex%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20he's%20from%20a%20wealthy%20family%20in%20Indonesia%20and%20earned%20a%20diploma%20from%20South%20Metropolitan%20TAFE%20in%20Perth%2C%20Australia.%20BI%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20information%20about%20his%20family's%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20he%20told%20the%20officer%20he%20was%20a%20flight%20attendant%20with%20Qatar%20Airways%2C%20but%20the%20officer%20refused%20to%20believe%20he%20could%20afford%20the%20items.%20Ignatius%20told%20BI%20the%20Irving%20loafers%2C%20Kelly%20belt%2C%20and%20Geta%20bag%20were%20all%20from%20Herm%C3%A8s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'you%20think%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20you%20earn%20every%20month%20and%20you%20think%20you%20can%20buy%20Herm%C3%A8s%3F'%26quot%3B%20Ignatius%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20when%20he%20told%20the%20officer%20he%20had%20purchased%20the%20items%20before%20working%20for%20the%20airline%2C%20the%20man%20slapped%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20he%20asked%20to%20contact%20the%20Indonesian%20embassy%20in%20Doha%2C%20but%20the%20officer%20refused%20and%20told%20him%20that%20he%20could%20wait%20in%20jail%2C%20as%20the%20embassies%20were%20closed.%20The%20Indonesian%20embassy%20in%20Doha%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20BI's%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20the%20officer%20later%20released%20him%2C%20and%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20Qatar%20Airways%20living%20quarters%20before%20a%204%20a.m.%20curfew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20police%20clearance%20certificate%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20the%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20said%20Ignatius%20had%20no%20previous%20criminal%20convictions.%20The%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20BI's%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%2C%20Ignatius%20said%20Qatar%20Airways%20confiscated%20his%20passport%20and%20that%20he%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20living%20quarters.%20Ignatius%20was%20then%20fired%20on%20June%204%2C%20according%20to%20a%20letter%20from%20Qatar%20Airways%20viewed%20by%20BI.%20The%20airline%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20BI's%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20he%20has%20since%20returned%20to%20Indonesia.%20He%20said%20he%20now%20works%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%20with%20Jetstar%2C%20owned%20by%20Australia's%20Qantas.%20Jetstar%20told%20BI%20that%20due%20to%20privacy%20reasons%2C%20confirmation%20of%20employment%20could%20not%20be%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgnatius%20said%20he's%20needed%20counseling%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20emotional%20stress%20of%20the%20incident%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20left%20in%20shock.%20I%20was%20traumatized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20Qatar%20has%20had%20several%20controversies%20related%20to%20its%20anti-LGBTQ%20stance.%20In%20September%202022%2C%20three%20men%20from%20the%20Phi