n%20Commission%20website.%20Add%20the%20total%20votes%20received%20by%20all%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20four%20states%20for%20which%20results%20were%20declared%20on%20December%203.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20blowing%20the%20trumpet%20of%20victory%2C%20has%20got%20a%20total%20of%204%2C81%2C33%2C463%20votes%2C%20whereas%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdefeated%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20has%20got%204%2C90%2C77907%20votes.%20That%20means%2C%20overall%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20got%20about%209.5%20lakhs%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20BJP.%20Still%2C%20all%20discussions%20seem%20to%20be%20assuming%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20completely%20destroyed%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20three%20Hindi-speaking%20states%20which%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%2C%20in%20fact%20there%20is%20not%20much%20difference%20in%20the%20number%20of%20votes.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20got%2041.7%25%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20has%20got%2039.6%25%20votes.%20The%20difference%2C%20then%2C%20is%20only%202%25.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%20the%20difference%20is%204%25%20%E2%80%93%20BJP%20has%2046.3%25%20votes%20while%20the%20Congress%20has%2042.2%25%20votes.%20Only%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20the%20difference%20a%20little%20higher%2C%20at%20more%20than%208%25%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20got%2048.6%25%20votes%20and%20Congress%2040%25%20votes.%20Despite%20losing%20in%20all%20three%20states%2C%20Congress%20has%20got%2040%25%20or%20more%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20from%20where%20it%20will%20not%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20make%20a%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20lead%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20got%20in%20all%20three%20Hindi-speaking%20states%20is%20compensated%20by%20only%20one%20Telangana.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20got%2039.4%25%20(more%20than%2092%20lakh)%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20got%2013.9%25%20(less%20than%2032%20lakh)%20votes.%20In%20a%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20was%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20out%20of%20the%20electoral%20race%20after%202018%2C%20the%20party%20reaching%20the%20top%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20political%20vitality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FKKn2SPGOUkc%3Fsi%3D1ulbXYRpUKJSKWVI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%202%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Look%20back%20on%20history%20to%20test%20the%20hat-trick%20myth.%20For%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20have%20been%20held%20within%20a%20few%20months%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20Last%20time%20in%202018%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20lost%20in%20these%20three%20states.%20But%20then%20neither%20the%20prime%20minister%20nor%20the%20media%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20was%20certain.%20When%20parliamentary%20elections%20were%20held%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20these%20three%20states%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20lost%20in%20these%20three%20states%20in%202003%2C%20it%20achieved%20an%20unexpected%20success%20in%20the%202004%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20just%20a%20few%20months%20later.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20nature%20of%20elections%20for%20assemblies%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20are%20different%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20wrong%20to%20draw%20conclusions%20about%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20directly%20from%20the%20assemblies.%20If%20the%20BJP%20can%20reverse%20this%20trend%2C%20then%20why%20not%20the%20Congress%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%203%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Look%20at%20the%20equation%20of%20change%20of%20power%20in%202024.%20The%20BJP%20is%20dependent%20on%20these%20three%20states%20of%20the%20Hindi%20belt%2C%20but%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20hopes%20do%20not%20rest%20on%20them.%20The%20electoral%20mathematics%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20depends%20on%20reducing%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20seats%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20Out%20of%2065%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20BJP%20already%20has%2061%20in%20its%20account%20and%20the%20Congress%20has%20only%20three.%20That%20means%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20challenge%20is%20to%20retain%20all%20these%20seats%20and%2C%20if%20possible%2C%20get%20more%20than%20the%20four%20seats%20it%20had%20won%20in%20Telangana.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20nothing%20to%20lose%20in%20these%20states.%20This%20means%20that%20from%20a%20national%20election%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20achieved%20anything%20new%20in%20these%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%204%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20How%20much%20do%20these%20legislative%20assemblies%20count%20for%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%3F%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20need%20to%20overturn%20these%20results%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram%20together%20have%2083%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20got%2065%20of%20these%20seats%3B%20only%20six%20went%20to%20the%20Congress.%20The%20rest%20went%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20and%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20get%20exactly%20the%20same%20number%20of%20votes%20in%20every%20assembly%20constituency%20as%20they%20got%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20then%20the%20figures%20will%20be%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%3A%20BJP%2014%20seats%2C%20Congress%2011%3Cbr%3E%5CnChhattisgarh%3A%20BJP%208%20seats%2C%20Congress%203%3Cbr%3E%5CnMadhya%20Pradesh%3A%20BJP%2025%20seats%2C%20Congress%204%3Cbr%3E%5CnTelangana%20%3A%20Congress%209%20seats%2C%20BJP%200%20(BRS%20gets%207%20and%20AIMIM%201)%3Cbr%3E%5CnMizoram%3A%20JMP%201%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20according%20to%20these%20assembly%20elections%2C%20out%20of%2083%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BJP%20gets%2046%20seats%20and%20Congress%20gets%2028%20seats.%20Meaning%2C%20instead%20of%20gain%2C%20according%20to%20these%20assembly%20results%2C%20BJP%20may%20suffer%20a%20loss%20of%2019%20seats%20while%20the%20Congress%20may%20gain%2022%20seats.%20All%20the%20Congress%20has%20to%20do%20is%20ensure%20that%20the%20votes%20it%20got%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20it%20also%20gets%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20some%20may%20say%20this%20is%20simple%20mathematics.%20You%20haven%E2%80%99t%20even%20accounted%20for%20%E2%80%9CModi%20magic%E2%80%9D.%20If%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20magic%20works%2C%20then%20a%20saffron%20wave%20will%20wash%20over%20all%20these%20states%20and%20the%20Congress%20will%20be%20wiped%20out.%20But%20if%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EModi%20hai%20to%20kuch%20bhi%20mumkin%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20if%20you%20believe%20in%20magic%20%E2%80%93%20then%20call%20it%20faith%2C%20what%20is%20the%20need%20to%20take%20cover%20from%20the%20results%20of%20assembly%20elections%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYogendra%20Yadav%20is%20a%20political%20activist%20and%20psephologist%2C%20and%20founder%20of%20Swaraj%20Abhiyan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701752039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05102221%2FGAesfmNbwAAba-E.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20how%20psychological