es%20replacing%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20Act%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%202023.%20The%20other%20Bills%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20in%20this%20session%20are%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%202023%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%202023%2C%20and%20legislation%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20election%20commissioners.%20A%20discussion%20is%20slated%20for%20the%20next%20week%20on%20the%20penal%20code%20Bill%20with%20between%2012-%2015%20hours%20set%20aside%20for%20discussion%20in%20both%20Houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20got%20a%20standing%20ovation%20from%20his%20party%20members%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%9CModi%20Modi%E2%80%9D%20echoing%20in%20the%20chamber%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building.%20Protests%20that%20such%20enthusiasm%20was%20best%20reserved%20for%20a%20party%20office%20drowned%20in%20the%20loud%20cheers%20and%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EModi%20ki%20sarkar%2C%20teesri%20baar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20poised%20for%20a%20third%20term)%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Along%20with%20home%20minister%20Amit%20shah%20and%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Modi%20watched%20the%20praise%20being%20showered%20silently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20was%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20report%20that%20was%20listed%20to%20be%20tabled%20Monday%20but%20never%20was%20because%20the%20Treasury%20Benches%20were%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20allow%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20to%20steal%20its%20thunder.%20TMC%20members%2C%20who%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Clukewarm%20response%E2%80%9D%20to%20Mahua%20Moitra%20till%20recently%2C%20rallied%20behind%20her%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20adjourning%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%20report%20has%20recommended%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Moitra%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccash-for-query%E2%80%9D%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20her%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey.%20Moitra%20told%20reporters%20she%20will%20comment%20once%20the%20report%20is%20tabled.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20her%20party%20chief%2C%20had%20in%20a%20nod%20of%20support%20broken%20her%20silence%20on%20the%20controversy%20recently.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Dubey%20has%20accused%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20TMC%20%3Cem%3Ebete%20noire%3C%2Fem%3E%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20of%20leaking%20the%20Ethics%20panel%20report%2C%20while%20Choudhury%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20that%20expulsion%20is%20too%20harsh%20a%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20reprieve%20for%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20whose%20suspension%20was%20reversed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Chadha%20apologised%20unconditionally%20and%20a%20motion%20was%20moved%20by%20BJP%20MP%20G.V.L.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20to%20revoke%20the%20suspension.%20Within%20a%20minute%20of%20his%20entry%20into%20the%20House%2C%20Chadha%20issued%20a%20video%20thanking%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20least%20for%20115%20days%2C%20I%20was%20suspended.%20During%20those%20days%2C%20I%20could%20not%20ask%20your%20questions%20inside%20Parliament%20and%20was%20not%20able%20to%20raise%20your%20voice%20inside%20the%20House%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20that%20my%20suspension%20was%20ended.%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20for%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChadha%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20House%20in%20August%20for%20breach%20of%20privilege%20of%20the%20House.%20Four%20MPs%20had%20complained%20about%20the%20breach%20of%20their%20privilege%20stating%20that%20their%20names%20had%20been%20included%20in%20an%20amendment%20moved%20by%20Chadha%20to%20refer%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20a%20Select%20Committee%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Post%20Office%20Bill%202023%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Advocates%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Monday%20before%20both%20Houses%20were%20adjourned%20to%20meet%20tomorrow.%20While%20the%20Advocates%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20touts%20in%20the%20various%20courts%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Postal%20Bill%20that%20will%20be%20viewed%20with%20concern.%20According%20to%20the%20proposed%20legislation%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20central%20government%20may%2C%20by%20notification%2C%20empower%20any%20officer%20to%20intercept%2C%20open%20or%20detain%20any%20item%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20security%20of%20the%20State%2C%20friendly%20relations%20with%20foreign%20states%2C%20public%20order%2C%20emergency%20or%20public%20safety%2C%20or%20upon%20the%20occurrence%20of%20any%20contravention%20of%20any%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20any%20law%20for%20the%20time%20being%20in%20force.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98This%20is%20an%20act%20of%20surveillance%20on%20citizens%2C%20fails%20to%20specify%20procedures%20and%20the%20grounds%20are%20very%20vague.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20are%20no%20consequences%20for%20the%20unauthorised%20opening%20of%20postal%20articles%20by%20a%20postal%20officer.%20This%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20articles%2019%20and%2021%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Shaktisinh%20Govil%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20demanded%2C%20during%20the%20session%2C%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20imbroglio%2C%20and%20the%20Indians%20on%20death%20row%20in%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701708459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28190125%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-6.59.30-PM_cleanup-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwinter-session-of-parliament-kicks-off-on-adjournment-note-two-bills-passed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20slated%20for%20the%20first%20day%20of%20this%20session%2C%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20Report%20on%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20recommending%20her%20expulsion%20from%20parliament%2C%20was%20not%20tabled%20on%20Monday%2C%20December%204.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwinter-session-of-parliament-kicks-off-on-adjournment-note-two-bills-passed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Respect%20the%20Science%20in%20Everything%20I%20Do%E2%80%99%2C%20Clarifies%20COP28%20Prez%3B%20India%20Skips%20Two%20Declarations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04204251%2FSultan.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20COP28%20president%20Sultan%20al-Jaber%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVaKKOSdtR50%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%20(December%204)%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceverything%20this%20presidency%20has%20been%20working%20on%20and%20continues%20to%20work%20on%20is%20focused%20on%20and%20centred%20around%20the%20science%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20have%20been%20crystal%20clear%20on%20that%20point%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20have%20always%20been%20very%20clear%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20are%20making%20sure%20that%20everything%20we%20do%20is%20centred%20around%20the%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20non-profit%20Centre%20for%20Climate%20Reporting%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20reported%20him%20as%20saying%20last%20month%20that%20there%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2023%2Fdec%2F03%2Fback-into-caves-cop28-president-dismisses-phase-out-of-fossil-fuels%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cno%20science%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prove%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20phase%20out%20fossil%20fuels%20in%20order%20to%20limit%20global%20warming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20factual%20and%20I%20respect%20the%20science%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20science%20out%20there%2C%20or%20no%20scenario%20out%20there%2C%20that%20says%20that%20the%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20is%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20achieve%201.5%20%5Bdegrees%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20an%20online%20conference%20on%20November%2021%2C%20calling%20such%20discussion%20%E2%80%9Calarmist%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Jaber%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20agreement%20among%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20governments%20in%202015%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-change-glossary-every-term-you-need-to-understand-explained%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98pursue%20efforts%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20limiting%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20%C2%B0C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9C1.5%20is%20my%20north%20star.%20A%20phase-down%20and%20a%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20is%20inevitable%2C%20it%20is%20essential%3B%20but%20we%20need%20to%20be%20real%2C%20serious%2C%20pragmatic%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67143989%5C%22%3Ephase-down%20of%20fossil%20fuel%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20refers%20to%20the%20gradual%20reduction%20in%20their%20use%20but%20not%20a%20complete%20stop%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20al-Jaber%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67612929%5C%22%3Ewho%20is%20trained%20as%20an%20engineer%20and%20economist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cscience%20has%20been%20central%20to%20my%20own%20career%20progress%20and%20yes%2C%20I%20respect%20the%20science%20in%20everything%20I%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BBC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20honestly%20think%20there%20is%20some%20confusion%20out%20there%2C%20and%20misrepresentation.%20I%20am%20quite%20surprised%20with%20the%20constant%20and%20repeated%20attempts%20to%20undermine%20the%20work%20of%20the%20COP28%20presidency%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20said%20according%20to%20the%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20phase-out%20of%20coal%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%20is%20proving%20to%20be%20controversial%20at%20the%20Dubai%20climate%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%C2%A0and%20several%20other%20countries%20have%20tried%20to%20shift%20the%20discussion%20to%20emerging%20technologies%20such%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcan-untested-carbon-removal-technology-beccs-help-deliver-climate-goals%2Fa-61639540%5C%22%3ECO%3Csub%3E2%3C%2Fsub%3E%20storage%20or%20capture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20arguing%20that%20fossil%20fuels%20can%20still%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20energy%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20experts%20have%20said%20these%20technologies%20are%20very%20expensive%20and%20cannot%20yet%20be%20scaled%20up%20to%20counter%20global%20heating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20science%20is%20clear.%20The%201.5%20degree%20target%20is%20only%20possible%20if%20we%20finally%20stop%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20at%20the%20start%20of%20COP28%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdeveloping-nations-should-be-given-fair-share-of-global-carbon-budget-pm-modi-at-cop28%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20Nations%20Should%20Be%20Given%20Fair%20Share%20of%20Global%20Carbon%20Budget%3A%20PM%20Modi%20at%20COP28%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20does%20not%20sign%20declarations%20on%20renewable%20energy%20and%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20100%20countries%20endorsed%20a%20pledge%20at%20the%20COP28%20meeting%20that%20was%20mainly%20about%20tripling%20renewable%20energy%20installed%20capacity%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20did%20not%20endorse%20this%20pledge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcoal-phase-out-in-cop28-pledge-india-refrains-from-endorsing-it-9053276%2F%5C%22%3Edue%20to%20references%20in%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98phase-out%E2%80%99%20of%20coal%20and%20to%20ending%20new%20investments%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.ec.europa.eu%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2F2023-12%2FGlobal_Renewables_and_Energy_Efficiency_Pledge.pdf%5C%22%3Edraft%20of%20the%20pledge%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20the%20deployment%20of%20renewables%20this%20decade%20must%20be%20accompanied%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cphase%20down%20of%20unabated%20coal%20power%2C%20in%20particular%20ending%20the%20continued%20investment%20in%20unabated%20new%20coal-fired%20power%20plants%2C%20which%20is%20incompatible%20with%20efforts%20to%20limit%20warming%20to%201.5%C2%B0C.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20goals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fenergy-and-environment%2Fcop28-climate-summit-india-will-not-be-bound-by-curbs-on-energy-use-environment-secretary%2Farticle67601493.ece%5C%22%3Erun%20contrary%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20long-standing%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20rely%20on%20coal%20power%20%E2%80%93%20its%20largest%20source%20of%20energy%20%E2%80%93%20to%20increase%20the%20standards%20of%20living%20for%20its%20population%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20did%20not%20sign%20a%20declaration%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%20on%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20one%20of%20points%20in%20the%20declaration%20relating%20to%20cooling%20in%20the%20health%20sector%20may%20not%20be%20achievable%20in%20India%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20cold%20storages%20for%20storing%20vaccines%20and%20medicines%20and%20these%20are%20linked%20to%20making%20our%20healthcare%20systems%20resilient%2C%E2%80%9D%20secretary%20of%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20Leena%20Nandan%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20suggestions%20that%20using%20these%20are%20contributing%20to%20climate%20emissions%20and%20that%20we%20must%20choose%20some%20fuels%20over%20the%20other%20are%20not%20acceptable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcop28-uae-president-we-very-much-believe-climate-science%2Fa-67624227%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701706380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04204251%2FSultan.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop-28-president-respect-science-india-declarations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20lack%20of%20endorsement%20for%20two%20declarations%20were%20because%20of%20references%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98phase-out%E2%80%99%20of%20coal%20power%20and%20what%20officials%20said%20were%20targets%20that%20are%20unviable%20for%20India's%20health%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop-28-president-respect-science-india-declarations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mukhtar%20Ansari's%20Family%20Moves%20SC%20for%20His%20Transfer%20from%20UP%20Jail%2C%20Cites%20'Immediate%20Threat'%20to%20His%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04211237%2FEffect-11.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20family%20of%20jailed%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20legislator%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20has%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20alleging%20that%20the%20state%20government%20run%20by%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20is%20planning%20to%20assassinate%20him%20in%20Banda%20jail%20where%20he%20is%20currently%20lodged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20Ansari%E2%80%99s%20younger%20son%2C%20Umar%20Ansari%2C%20has%20sought%20protection%20for%20his%20father%20from%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20transfer%20from%20the%20Banda%20jail.%20Mukhtar%20faces%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20and%20grave%20threat%20to%20his%20life%20and%20limb%E2%80%9D%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20said%20Umar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-time%20former%20MLA%20from%20Mau%20in%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Mukhtar%20has%20for%20long%20been%20under%20the%20radar%20of%20the%20Adityanath%20government%2C%20which%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202017%20unleashed%20the%20police%20and%20the%20force%20of%20the%20administration%20against%20him%2C%20his%20family%2C%20and%20supporters.%20While%20Mukhtar%2C%20despite%20his%20notoriety%20and%20a%20long%20list%20of%20criminal%20cases%20lodged%20against%20him%20over%20the%20years%2C%20continued%20to%20enjoy%20the%20image%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Robin%20Hood%E2%80%99%20politician%20who%20took%20on%20the%20feudal%20forces%20of%20Purvanchal.%20However%2C%20all%20that%20changed%20once%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20stormed%20to%20power%20six%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmla-mukhtar-ansari-prison-congress-ajay-rai%5C%22%3EEx-MLA%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20Gets%2010%20Years%20in%20Prison%20Over%20Murder%20of%20Congress%20Leader%E2%80%99s%20Brother%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20designated%20Mukhtar%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgangster%E2%80%9D%20and%20head%20of%20gang%20IS191%20and%20lodged%20numerous%20criminal%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20his%20sons%2C%20including%20current%20MLA%20Abbas%20Ansari%2C%20his%20brother%20and%20former%20MP%20Afzal%20Ansari%20and%20other%20associates.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20seized%2C%20demolished%2C%20and%20freed%20from%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20occupation%E2%80%9D%20crores%20worth%20of%20property%20belonging%20to%20the%20Ansari%20family%20under%20the%20stringent%20Gangsters%20Act%20and%20eliminated%20several%20persons%20considered%20close%20to%20the%20former%20MLA%20in%20alleged%20shootouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Reliable%20information%E2%80%99%20available%20of%20%E2%80%98assassination%E2%80%99%20plot%2C%20says%20Ansari%E2%80%99s%20son%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPetitioner%20Umar%20Ansari%20also%20expressed%20concern%20for%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20well-being%20by%20drawing%20attention%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20tainted%20politician%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fatiq-ahmed-adityanath-uttar-pradesh-police-encounter%5C%22%3EAtiq%20Ahmad%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20brother%20Ashraf%20Ahmad%20on%20live%20television%20while%20they%20were%20being%20escorted%20by%20a%20team%20of%20policemen%20for%20a%20routine%20medical%20check-up%20in%20Prayagraj%20on%20April%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F16144735%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.02.58-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F16144735%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.02.58-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F16144735%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.02.58-PM-300x169.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F16144735%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.02.58-PM-1024x576.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-648838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAtiq%20and%20Ashraf%20Ahmed%20moments%20before%20they%20were%20killed.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20before%20the%20brothers%20were%20murdered%20by%20three%20mysterious%20assailants%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20police%20%E2%80%93who%20despite%20being%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire%20for%20reasons%20known%20to%20them%20did%20not%20shoot%20the%20culprits%20in%20self-defence%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20dismissed%20Atiq%E2%80%99s%20plea%20seeking%20protection%20during%20his%20custody%20with%20the%20UP%20police%20in%20the%20Umesh%20Pal%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmesh%20Pal%20was%20a%20key%20witness%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20MLA%20Raju%20Pal%2C%20in%20which%20the%20ex-MP%20and%20ex-MLA%20were%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Umar%2C%20accused%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20of%20taking%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinimical%20position%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20former%20MLA%20and%20hatching%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20to%20eliminate%20him%20while%20he%20is%20in%20jail.%20The%20threat%20perception%20is%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Creliable%20information%E2%80%9D%20Mukhtar%20has%20received%20that%20his%20life%20is%20in%20grave%20danger%20and%20that%20there%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20conspiracy%20afoot%20involving%20several%20actors%20within%20the%20state%20establishment%E2%80%9D%20to%20assassinate%20him%20in%20Banda%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmar%20provides%20a%20graphic%20depiction%20of%20the%20way%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99s%20family%20fears%20he%20might%20be%20murdered.%20The%20same%20modus%20operandi%20had%20been%20used%20to%20carry%20out%20killings%20in%20jail%20in%20several%20other%20cases%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20petitioner%20said%20that%20a%20number%20of%20persons%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Krishnanand%20Rai%20in%202005%20%E2%80%93%20Mukhtar%20was%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20a%20related%20case%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20killed%20by%20the%20Special%20Task%20Force%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police%20in%20similar%20circumstances.%20Even%20though%20Mukhtar%20and%20other%20accused%20persons%20had%20been%20acquitted%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Krishnanand%20Rai%2C%20they%20are%20still%20viewed%20as%20culprits%20and%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%20have%20time%20and%20again%20sworn%20vengeance%20against%20them%20from%20public%20platforms%2C%20said%20Umar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicted%20politician%E2%80%99s%20son%20said%20that%20out%20of%20the%20persons%20accused%20of%20murdering%20Rai%2C%20four%20had%20already%20been%20murdered.%20While%20Firdaus%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20the%20STF%20in%202006%2C%20Prem%20Prakash%20Singh%20alias%20Munna%20Bajrangi%20was%20murdered%20in%20Baghpat%20jail%20in%202018%20by%20another%20convicted%20gangster%20Sunil%20Rathi.%20More%20than%20a%20week%20before%20his%20murder%20Bajrangi%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Seema%20Singh%20had%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20June%2029%20that%20year%20alleged%20that%20the%20UP%20police%20along%20with%20some%20political%20leaders%20and%20officials%20were%20conspiring%20to%20get%20him%20eliminated%20outside%20the%20jail%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20encounter%E2%80%9D.%20Singh%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20during%20his%20stay%20in%20Jhansi%20jail%2C%20there%20had%20been%20an%20attempt%20to%20poison%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aide%20of%20Mukhtar%2C%20Rakesh%20Pandey%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20the%20police%20in%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%E2%80%9D%20in%20August%202020%20after%20the%20SUV%20he%20was%20purportedly%20travelling%20in%20along%20with%20four%20other%20persons%20crashed%20into%20a%20tree%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20a%20Sunday%20morning.%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20picking%20him%20up%20from%20home%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20then%20killing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20Sanjeev%20Maheshwari%20alias%20Jeeva%2C%20an%20alleged%20associate%20of%20Mukhtar%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20inside%20a%20courtroom%20in%20Lucknow%20while%20he%20was%20being%20produced%20before%20the%20court.%20Jeeva%20had%20also%20been%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Brahm%20Dutt%20Dwivedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99s%20son%20also%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20of%20covering%20up%20the%20murder%20of%20one%20Meraj%2C%20who%20had%20been%20a%20co-accused%20of%20Mukhtar%20in%20a%20MCOCA%20case%2C%20in%20which%20both%20were%20acquitted.%20In%20May%202021%2C%20an%20inmate%20of%20the%20Chitrakoot%20jail%20Anshu%20Dikshit%20allegedly%20shot%20dead%20Mukim%20Kala%20and%20Meraj%20with%20a%20firearm%2C%20inside%20the%20prison.%20Dikshit%2C%20who%20was%20lodged%20in%20a%20high-security%20barrack%2C%20was%20later%20shot%20dead%20by%20police%20after%20he%20allegedly%20held%20hostage%20five%20other%20inmates%20and%20threatened%20to%20kill%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20was%20in%20power%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20Opposition%20party%20had%20alleged%20that%20Hindus%20in%20Kairana%2C%20in%20western%20UP%2C%20were%20being%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20due%20to%20the%20fear%20of%20and%20intimidation%20by%20Mukim%20Kala%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20gang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%202021%2C%20Mukim%20Kala%E2%80%99s%20mother%20had%20approached%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20seeking%20protection%20for%20him%20when%20he%20had%20been%20detained%20in%20Saharanpur%20jail.%20She%20alleged%20that%20the%20police%20were%20harassing%20Mukim%20by%20trying%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20her%20to%20withdraw%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20her%20against%20the%20police%20after%20her%20younger%20son%20Wasim%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20alleged%20encounter%20in%202017.%20In%20March%202021%2C%20the%20HC%20noted%20that%20the%20response%20from%20the%20government%20did%20not%20show%20any%20harassment%20of%20her%20son%20but%20directed%20the%20state%20to%20see%20that%20no%20harm%20was%20caused%20to%20Kala%20and%20to%20conduct%20operations%20as%20per%20the%20jail%20manual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20of%20%E2%80%98murders%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20public%20submissions%20by%20politicians%20and%20even%20accused%20criminals%20about%20threats%20to%20their%20lives%20are%20often%20taken%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%2C%20the%20frequency%20and%20brazenness%20of%20such%20murders%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20make%20it%20necessary%20to%20reproduce%20the%20details%20of%20the%20threat%20perceived%20by%20these%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn-300x129.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn-1024x439.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22515%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUP%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20at%20the%20Police%20Smriti%20Diwas%20event%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20October%2021%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40myogiadityanath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Umar%20Ansari%20noted%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20information%20received%20from%20reliable%20sources%20within%20the%20police%20establishment%2C%20the%20persons%20who%20have%20been%20hired%20to%20assassinate%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20father%20shall%20be%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20or%20summoned%20on%20remand%20in%20some%20petty%20crime%2C%20produced%20before%20the%20court%20and%20then%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody.%20Then%2C%20they%20shall%20be%20taken%20to%20Banda%20Jail%20where%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20father%20is%20currently%20lodged.%20This%20shall%20give%20the%20said%20persons%20the%20desired%20proximity%20to%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20father.%20Thereafter%2C%20these%20hired%20killers%20will%20be%20provided%20access%20to%20arms%20inside%20jail%20and%20an%20opportunity%20by%20way%20of%20a%20lapse%20in%20security%20systems%20that%20they%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20through%20complicit%20jail%20officials.%20The%20standard%20mode%20of%20operation%20is%20to%20give%20the%20attack%20the%20color%20of%20a%20fight%20between%20the%20inmates%20in%20order%20to%20give%20the%20entire%20incident%20the%20misleading%20cover%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98gang-war%E2%80%99%20(sic).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsince-adityanath-took-over-in-2017-up-police-have-killed-190-people-in-encounters%5C%22%3ESince%20Adityanath%20Took%20Over%20in%202017%2C%20UP%20Police%20Have%20Killed%20190%20People%20in%20%E2%80%98Encounters%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhtar%20faces%20more%20than%2060%20criminal%20cases%20and%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%2C%20he%20has%20been%20convicted%20in%20six%20cases.%20This%20included%20the%20life%20sentence%20awarded%20to%20him%20by%20a%20Varanasi%20court%20in%20June%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Awadesh%20Rai%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20Congress%20state%20president%20Ajay%20Rai%2C%20and%20the%2010%20years%20imprisonment%20awarded%20to%20him%20for%20kidnapping%20a%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20leader%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20Krishnanand%20Rai%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhtar%20was%20born%20in%20Ghazipur%20district%20in%20East%20UP%2C%20bordering%20Varanasi.%20His%20family%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20he%20grew%20up%20with%20a%20Communist%20legacy%20through%20his%20grandfather%20and%20father.%20In%20his%20political%20career%2C%20Mukhtar%20and%20his%20brother%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20both%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20treated%20him%20as%20the%20mascot%20of%20criminal%20politics%20and%20went%20after%20him%20through%20criminal%20cases.%20However%2C%20this%20took%20a%20sharp%20turn%20in%20July%202020%20when%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20was%20pushed%20to%20the%20backfoot%20after%20the%20Bikru%20incident%20in%20Kanpur%20where%20eight%20policemen%20were%20shot%20dead%20by%20history-sheeter%20Vikash%20Dubey%20and%20his%20associates.%20Dubey%20and%20several%20of%20his%20men%20were%20later%20shot%20dead%20by%20police%20in%20alleged%20encounters%2C%20with%20unsettled%20questions%20being%20raised%20over%20their%20genuineness.%20In%20terms%20of%20electoral%20politics%2C%20this%20was%20also%20a%20crisis%20for%20the%20BJP%20government%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20influential%20Brahmin%20community.%C2%A0%20To%20placate%20them%20and%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20Bikru%20massacre%2C%20the%20state%20government%20unleashed%20a%20wave%20of%20punitive%20measures%20against%20other%20controversial%20figures%20in%20state%20politics%2C%20most%20prominent%20among%20them%20Mukhtar%2C%20who%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20a%20Muslim%2C%20fitted%20perfectly%20into%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20polarising%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701706367000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc